            <description><![CDATA[<p STYLE="TexT-inDenT: 24pt; MArGin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0">
<strong><span STYLE="FonT-siZe: 12pt; FonT-WeiGHT: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"><font COLOR="#2F3699" FACE="Times New Roman">下文是博主在<span LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">2011</SPAN><font FACE="宋体">年<span LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">1</SPAN>月<span LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US">14</SPAN>日凌晨完成的</FONT>《英才》杂志约稿，发表于刚刚出版的2011年2月该杂志上：</FONT></SPAN></STRONG></P>
<p STYLE="TexT-inDenT: 24pt; MArGin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" ALIGN="center"><span STYLE="FonT-siZe: 12pt; FonT-WeiGHT: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"><strong><font COLOR="#2F3699">2011年真的很复杂吗？</FONT></STRONG></SPAN></P>
<p STYLE="TexT-inDenT: 24pt; MArGin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0">
<font COLOR="#2F3699"><strong><span STYLE="FonT-siZe: 12pt; FonT-WeiGHT: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"><font FACE="Times New Roman">2010</FONT></SPAN></STRONG><strong><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 12pt; FonT-WeiGHT: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">年，中国</SPAN></STRONG><strong><span STYLE="FonT-siZe: 12pt; FonT-WeiGHT: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"><font FACE="Times New Roman">A</FONT></SPAN></STRONG><strong><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 12pt; FonT-WeiGHT: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">股走势偏弱，沪综指全年下跌</SPAN></STRONG><strong><span STYLE="FonT-siZe: 12pt; FonT-WeiGHT: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"><font FACE="Times New Roman">469</FONT></SPAN></STRONG><strong><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 12pt; FonT-WeiGHT: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">点，跌幅达到</SPAN></STRONG><strong><span STYLE="FonT-siZe: 12pt; FonT-WeiGHT: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"><font FACE="Times New Roman">14.31%</FONT></SPAN></STRONG><strong><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 12pt; FonT-WeiGHT: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">，投资者在失望之余，对已经拉开大幕的</SPAN></STRONG><strong><span STYLE="FonT-siZe: 12pt; FonT-WeiGHT: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"><font FACE="Times New Roman">2011</FONT></SPAN></STRONG><strong><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 12pt; FonT-WeiGHT: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">年行情又充满了期待，很多专业人士称今年将是“形式最复杂”的一年，新的一年行情真的很复杂吗？</SPAN></STRONG>
</FONT></P>
<p STYLE="TexT-inDenT: 24.1pt; MArGin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0">
<font COLOR="#2F3699"><strong><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
百川的观点是：中国股市在</SPAN></STRONG><strong><span STYLE="FonT-siZe: 12pt" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"><font FACE="Times New Roman">2011</FONT></SPAN></STRONG><strong><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">年有望震荡攀升，经过</SPAN></STRONG><strong><span STYLE="FonT-siZe: 12pt" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"><font FACE="Times New Roman">2010</FONT></SPAN></STRONG><strong><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">年的弱势整理之后，将在低估值的蓝筹股带领下，再度拉出年线的中阳甚至大阳，沪综指运行区间为</SPAN></STRONG><strong><span STYLE="FonT-siZe: 12pt" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"><font FACE="Times New Roman">2700</FONT></SPAN></STRONG><strong><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">点</SPAN></STRONG><strong><span STYLE="FonT-siZe: 12pt" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"><font FACE="Times New Roman">-5500</FONT></SPAN></STRONG><strong><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">点，上半年的热门板块是具备高增长特征、具有高送配年报预期的中小市值中小板和创业板个股，下半年热点将是沪深</SPAN></STRONG><strong><span STYLE="FonT-siZe: 12pt" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"><font FACE="Times New Roman">300</FONT></SPAN></STRONG><strong><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">当中的大盘蓝筹股，煤炭、有色等资源类个股也有不错的表现机会。</SPAN></STRONG></FONT></P>
<p STYLE="TexT-inDenT: 24pt; MArGin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0">
<font COLOR="#2F3699"><strong><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 12pt; FonT-WeiGHT: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
虽然美国对世界的影响力趋于减弱，但其仍是世界上的唯一超级大国，要分析预测世界经济的趋势，还是要先看美国。经历了</SPAN></STRONG><strong><span STYLE="FonT-siZe: 12pt; FonT-WeiGHT: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"><font FACE="Times New Roman">09</FONT></SPAN></STRONG><strong><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 12pt; FonT-WeiGHT: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">年和</SPAN></STRONG><strong><span STYLE="FonT-siZe: 12pt; FonT-WeiGHT: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"><font FACE="Times New Roman">10</FONT></SPAN></STRONG><strong><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 12pt; FonT-WeiGHT: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">年的缓慢复苏，美国经济逐渐出现了增长态势，道琼斯指数也在近期创出近两年来新高。同时，为了刺激经济的增长和提高产品的出口竞争力，泛滥的流动性和弱势美元政策的持续，使得美元指数的走势与股指走势背道而驰，若美元持续下跌，则商品价格在美元下跌和美国经济增长的双重利多影响下，有望在</SPAN></STRONG><strong><span STYLE="FonT-siZe: 12pt; FonT-WeiGHT: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"><font FACE="Times New Roman">2011</FONT></SPAN></STRONG><strong><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 12pt; FonT-WeiGHT: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">年迭创新高！</SPAN></STRONG></FONT></P>
<p STYLE="TexT-inDenT: 24pt; MArGin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0">
<font COLOR="#2F3699"><strong><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 12pt; FonT-WeiGHT: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
我们再回头看看中国国内的情况，</SPAN></STRONG><strong><span STYLE="FonT-siZe: 12pt; FonT-WeiGHT: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"><font FACE="Times New Roman">GDP</FONT></SPAN></STRONG><strong><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 12pt; FonT-WeiGHT: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">的增长毫无悬念，无疑使得上市公司会从中受益。全国人民都颇为担心的通胀问题，其实大可不必过于看重，毕竟，温和通胀对经济和股市的良性刺激作用是毋庸置疑的，恶性通胀能否出现呢？对这个问题，要从“讲政治”的角度看，只要相信中国党和政府的执政能力，牢记“稳定”与“和谐”的宗旨，就无需担心恶性通胀的出现。至于货币政策的紧缩，也不必害怕，只要看看房地产市场在多次调控和利空消息背景下的表现（</SPAN></STRONG><strong><span STYLE="FonT-siZe: 12pt; FonT-WeiGHT: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"><font FACE="Times New Roman">2010</FONT></SPAN></STRONG><strong><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 12pt; FonT-WeiGHT: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">年底到</SPAN></STRONG><strong><span STYLE="FonT-siZe: 12pt; FonT-WeiGHT: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"><font FACE="Times New Roman">2011</FONT></SPAN></STRONG><strong><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 12pt; FonT-WeiGHT: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">年初，房价再度上涨），就知道市场上的钱，实在是太多了。除了房价以外，</SPAN></STRONG><strong><span STYLE="FonT-siZe: 12pt; FonT-WeiGHT: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"><font FACE="Times New Roman">2010</FONT></SPAN></STRONG><strong><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 12pt; FonT-WeiGHT: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">年出现的“蒜你狠”、“姜你军”、“豆你玩”等等暴涨的农产品、价格疯狂上涨的和田玉、茅台酒等等，无一不说明一个事实：市场里面的钱，真的太多了！资金总是要逐利的，国内的大量热钱加上在美元贬值、人民币升值背景下涌入的国际热钱，两股洪流汇合之后，总要找到宣泄的去处，而除了股市以外，哪里去找更大更好的“池子”呢？</SPAN></STRONG></FONT></P>
<p STYLE="TexT-inDenT: 24pt; MArGin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0">
<font COLOR="#2F3699"><strong><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 12pt; FonT-WeiGHT: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
从市场板块来看，金融、地产等大市值板块估值偏低，封杀了指数向下的空间，使得</SPAN></STRONG><strong><span STYLE="FonT-siZe: 12pt; FonT-WeiGHT: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"><font FACE="Times New Roman">2011</FONT></SPAN></STRONG><strong><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 12pt; FonT-WeiGHT: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">年年初点位成为全年低位的概率极大，</SPAN></STRONG><strong><span STYLE="FonT-siZe: 12pt; FonT-WeiGHT: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"><font FACE="Times New Roman">2600-2700</FONT></SPAN></STRONG><strong><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 12pt; FonT-WeiGHT: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">点区域支撑力度很强，有望成为年度低点；在</SPAN></STRONG><strong><span STYLE="FonT-siZe: 12pt; FonT-WeiGHT: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"><font FACE="Times New Roman">2010</FONT></SPAN></STRONG><strong><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 12pt; FonT-WeiGHT: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">年下半年，中小板指数和创业板指数均创出历史新高，显示主流资金对其的介入程度很深，而这些资金显然是冲着该类股票良好的成长性来的，根据历史经验，最后的疯狂拉高行情及出货动作一定在年报公布前后，这也注定了今年上半年的热点仍将是中小市值股票，特别是有高送配的个股。而下半年，将成为大盘蓝筹股的表演时间，在良好业绩的支持下，在强烈补涨要求下，在把中小散户的筹码在低位“骗出”（诱使其高位追入中小盘股完成错误的换股）之后，就轮到“大象们”登台表演了，届时必将再度出现“二八现象”，在大市值个股的推动下，沪综指一路上涨，具体能涨到什么位置？一定是一个大家都不敢相信并且很多人预测不到的一个位置。从技术上看，沪综指自</SPAN></STRONG><strong><span STYLE="FonT-siZe: 12pt; FonT-WeiGHT: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"><font FACE="Times New Roman">08</FONT></SPAN></STRONG><strong><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 12pt; FonT-WeiGHT: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">年</SPAN></STRONG><strong><span STYLE="FonT-siZe: 12pt; FonT-WeiGHT: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"><font FACE="Times New Roman">10</FONT></SPAN></STRONG><strong><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 12pt; FonT-WeiGHT: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">月以来，进行了一个大的三角形整理，向上突破之后的理论目标在</SPAN></STRONG><strong><span STYLE="FonT-siZe: 12pt; FonT-WeiGHT: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"><font FACE="Times New Roman">4500</FONT></SPAN></STRONG><strong><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 12pt; FonT-WeiGHT: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">点附近，但是股市从来不会是依照技术分析的理性走势，要么涨过头、要么跌过头，所以<strong>博主大胆预测</STRONG></SPAN></STRONG><span><strong><font STYLE="FonT-siZe: 16px">2011年高点将是低点的翻番位置：5500点！</FONT></STRONG></SPAN></FONT></P>
<p STYLE="TexT-inDenT: 24pt; MArGin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0">
<strong><span STYLE="FonT-siZe: 12pt; FonT-WeiGHT: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"><font COLOR="#2F3699" FACE="Times New Roman">&nbsp;</FONT></SPAN></STRONG></P>
<p STYLE="TexT-inDenT: 24pt; MArGin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0">
<strong><span STYLE="FonT-siZe: 12pt; FonT-WeiGHT: normal; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold" LANG="EN-US" XML:LANG="EN-US"><font COLOR="#2F3699" FACE="Times New Roman">&nbsp;</FONT></SPAN></STRONG></P>
<p STYLE="MArGin: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><font COLOR="#2F3699"><span STYLE="FonT-FAMiLY: 宋体; FonT-siZe: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times new roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times new roman'">
